Interface IWorksheetStorage


  • public interface IWorksheetStorage
    Represents a container of services used to read or change the contents of the worksheet

    Works with single cells or ranges of cells

    • Method Detail

      • getCommonFont

        IFont getCommonFont(IRangeAddress range)
        Gets the aggregated font styles for the given range

        This method finds the differences between the cell fonts in the specified range.

        This method sets the identical values of the compared font attributes to the returned IFont instance. When the differences between the compared font attributes are detected, the method sets the value of the detected difference in the returned IFont instance to null

        Parameters:
        range - the range in which the comparison takes place
        Returns:
        the aggregated IFont structure

      • getCommonStyle

        IStyle getCommonStyle(IRangeAddress range)
        Aggregate styles to some structure

        This method finds the differences between the cell styles in the specified range

        This method sets the identical values of the compared cell style attributes to the returned IStyle instance. When the differences between the compared cell styles attributes are detected, the method sets the value of the detected difference in the returned IStyle instance to null

        Parameters:
        range - the range in which the comparison takes place
        Returns:
        the aggregated IStyle structure
